    "content": "-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\t\t\t Numb/Encore - Linkin Park & Jay-z  \r\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nTabbed By :yan_halen \r\ne-mail: ozprey_utd89@hotmail.com\r\n\r\nTuning: Standard (E A D G)\r\n\r\n(Hold 2.5 seconds for every note)\r\n\r\nIts damn easy.A little different from the original Linkin Park's NUMB.Thanx to my \r\nfriend Hasyim for the aid.\r\n\r\n[tab]INTRO\r\n[0:11]\r\nG|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------|\r\nE|2------------------5------------------| x2[/tab]\r\n\r\nGet em' Jay..\r\n\r\n[tab]RIFF 1\r\n[0:29]\r\nG|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------5---------------------------|\r\nE|2-------------------5---------0-------|x2[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]RIFF 2\r\n[0:47]\r\nG|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------|\r\nA|------------------------------4-------|\r\nE|2---------4---------5-----------------|x2[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]RIFF 3[CHORUS]\r\nG|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------5---------------------------|\r\nE|2-------------------5---------0-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------|\r\nA|----------5-------------------7-------|\r\nE|2-------------------5-----------------|[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]What the hell are you waiting for..\r\n[1:23]\r\nG|--------------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------------5---------0-------|[/tab]\r\n\r\nNow repeat RIFF 1 then RIFF 2\r\n\r\nPlay RIFF 3 on Chester's part\r\n\r\nThen play RIFF 2 then repeat RIFF3 till end of song.",
